name: NIMH SHAMAN Team skate Complete
description:
Roll the line between good and evil with the new SHAMAN skate from NIMH. Combining mystical properties of strength and style, the SHAMAN features a sleek, new over-skin, the latest NIMH soul plates, new bomb-proof NIMH liner, This is the skate preferred by team riders Montre Livingston, Joey Chase, John Bolino and Brian Shima. From the shadows comes a glimpse of your future… as foreseen by the SHAMAN.

Features include:
- upgraded cuff system with improved buckle protector
- newly designed extra comfortable Shaman liner
- high end Ground Control FLT 2 frames
- high velocity 608ZZ Abec 5 bearings
- Nimh 58mm/90a wheels.
